node.text:
TheWeedTube is proud to welcome the Brazilian community to our platform!

In this interview @rjthecunning and @tomazine420 talk about cannabis law in Brazil, why Brazilians are so fond of TheWeedTube, and much more!

This video has been captioned in Portuguese for our Brazilian viewers to enjoy as well! Please go watch and thank you for helping TheWeedTube support communities around the world in their fight against cannabis criminalization.

node.text:
SUPPRESSION IS ALIVE AND WELL 🚨 
.
.
It is unfortunate we have to put out posts like this so frequently, but censorship is an uphill battle.  Various platforms are consistently trying to curb the spread of content that includes valuable information and Instagram is the latest to ramp up their antics. This could be a major reason why you’re not seeing some of your favorite creators’ content. We changed our settings to allow more content to thrive, will you change yours? 🤔

Because censorship is nothing new to us (and we’re a platform created by people who were censored) we’ve resorted to alternative means of community alerts. Comment “Sign me up!” If you want us to send you an invite to our community Telegram. The Telegram chat is used to give updates that might have otherwise been censored by other social platforms. Sign up and don’t miss any updates! It’s a small team so please be patient as we work to get everyone in the group 💚 Share this post! Don’t let Instagram suppress us anymore than they already have! 
.
.
#suppression #censorship #contentcreators #artistsupport #communityalert #importantmessage
